"title": "5361: justice, human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5361",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God created the world in justice, and expects that his creatures will deal fairly and justly with one another as a result.  Sin brings injustice into the world, by disrupting the justice established by God at creation.  As a result, human justice often falls short of God's standards.</p>\n<h2>God shows his concern for human justice</h2>\n<h3>By commanding it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1\">ISA 56:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:1-Exod23:9\">EXO 23:1–23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:17\">DEU 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3\">PSA 82:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:6\">HOS 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:7\">ROM 13:7</a></p>\n<h3>By commending its maintenance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:3\">PSA 106:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:5-Gen20:6\">GEN 20:5–20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:11-1Kgs3:12\">1KI 3:11–3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:28\">1KI 3:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:8\">JOB 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:37\">PSA 37:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:5\">PSA 112:5</a></p>\n<h3>By condemning its neglect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:19\">DEU 27:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:13-Job31:14\">JOB 31:13–31:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:14\">ISA 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:15\">ISA 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:1\">ISA 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:5-Jer7:8\">JER 7:5–7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:14\">JER 7:14</a> <em>destruction follows ignored warnings</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:29-Ezek22:31\">EZK 22:29–22:31</a></p>\n<h2>Justice in relationships within the family</h2>\n<h3>Parents and children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:4\">MAT 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:1–6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20-Col3:21\">COL 3:20–3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:4\">1TI 3:4</a></p>\n<h3>Brothers and sisters</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:9-Gen4:10\">GEN 4:9–4:10</a></p>\n<h3>Husband and wife</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:14\">MAL 2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:4-1Cor7:5\">1CO 7:4–7:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:18-Col3:19\">COL 3:18–3:19</a></p>\n<h2>Justice in the community</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:7\">PRO 29:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:16\">JOB 29:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3\">PSA 82:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:14\">PRO 29:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:8-Prov31:9\">PRO 31:8–31:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:17\">ISA 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:16\">JER 22:16</a></p>\n<h2>Justice in the business world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:1\">COL 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:35-Lev19:36\">LEV 19:35–19:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:15\">DEU 25:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:9\">EPH 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:4\">JAS 5:1–5:4</a></p>\n<h2>Justice in courts of law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:6-Exod23:8\">EXO 23:6–23:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:15\">LEV 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:16\">DEU 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:18-Deut16:20\">DEU 16:18–16:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:6\">DEU 17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:1-Deut25:3\">DEU 25:1–25:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:25\">DEU 27:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:5-2Chr19:7\">2CH 19:5–19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:17\">PRO 12:17</a>PRO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:5\">18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:23-Prov24:25\">PRO 24:23–24:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:21\">PRO 28:21</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:17\">PRO 18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:23\">JHN 18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:3\">ACT 23:3</a></p>\n<h2>Justice in rulers and governments</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:15\">PRO 8:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:9\">1KI 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:14\">1CH 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:12-Prov16:13\">PRO 16:12–16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:26-Prov29:27\">PRO 29:26–29:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:8-Prov31:9\">PRO 31:8–31:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13-Jer22:16\">JER 22:13–22:16</a> <em>judgment against the son of King Josiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:9\">EZK 45:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1-Rom13:4\">ROM 13:1–13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Justice in the community of faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:6-Isa58:7\">ISA 58:6–58:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:6\">HOS 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:1-1Cor6:8\">1CO 6:1–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:12-Jas2:13\">JAS 2:12–2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Justice in a believer's life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8\">PHP 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:12\">TIT 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:16\">1PE 3:16</a></p>",
